5:23 For the husband is head of the wife, as Messiah also is head of His community—Himself the Savior of the body. 
5:24 But as Messiah’s community is submitted to Messiah, so also the wives to their husbands in everything. 
5:25 Husbands, love your wives just as Messiah also loved His community and gave Himself up for her 
